00:01:44.124 --> 00:01:45.790
This is the beginning
of a long journey,

00:01:45.790 --> 00:01:48.400
and it's only with the
enthusiasm and passion

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.610
of people like
those in this room

00:01:50.610 --> 00:01:52.840
