00:24:10.510 --> 00:24:14.360
easily build some of
these different civic apps

00:24:14.360 --> 00:24:18.510
with much less startup cost.

00:24:18.510 --> 00:24:20.520
So that's a little
bit about some

00:24:20.520 --> 00:24:22.540
of the work our team is
