00:24:22.540 --> 00:24:25.859
on the democratic
process easier to access.

00:24:25.859 --> 00:24:27.900
There are some of the
tools that we talked about.

00:24:27.900 --> 00:24:29.358
If you're interested
in this space,

00:24:29.358 --> 00:24:31.190
I hope you'll take a
